If you want to do anything please tell me and ill try to do it....im so bored.

They were both really fun.  so now im trying to scrub afro gel and whatever else is in revolution off my self.  Its gross.

Its over....you know what im talkin about...call if you want to do anything.  God it feels good to say that.  I already filled my weekend w/ doin stuff but considering its been six weeks, i think it wouldnt hurt to tack some activities on next week...so just talk to me and we'll find somn to do.

Tired...gonna study then sleep...but i have to get up for morning practice tommorow.  Nothing happened today thats worth talkin ab so im out.
Peace

Havn't updated in a while.  AP exam was last week, I think it went well.  Now im on to studying for the SAT IIs.  Other than that and swimming not much has been goin on.  Last weekend I was up in UNC with my Latin class.  Me, Emily, Kourtney, and Grant hung out with some kids from random schools.  we played ultimate, ate at mcalisters alot, played poker till like 2 am etc. It was cool.  So the NSS meet was this weekend, and so far im doing well...so im goin to sleep...my neck is getting really stiff.

tonight was supposed to be awesome.  we had the dance/party thing and it was gonna be a ton of fun.  But then like ten minutes into i have to go home because i was grounded a week ago for two weeks.  so my parents, who ususally never ground, just lecture me decide that i cant go. so im stuck at home studying instead of dancing w/ someone.

im exhausted.
i still have a lot of hw to do, and ive spent the last 2 nights in a tent in 34 degree weather in the mountains so my bed looks really soft and warm right now.  yeaaahh....im gonna go do hw in my bed.

LIFE CAN BE SO BORING.  I need a good dose of fun right now.  Im going camping this wknd so thatll spruce things up a little.  IM starting to get a little po'd about losing my phone, because this is my second one and my mom says im not gettin another one till i get my license if i dont find it. so call it and tell whoever has it to give it back because they wont listen to me...either that or noone has it and its out of batteries. so a couple nights ago, monday, was the worst night ever. it was just bad...dont ask. 
This is like the busyiest week of the year in my family since there are three birthdays within 5 days of each other. Im gettin sick of cake, and Golf clubs...my dad bought them all new sets of clubs since we are joining a golf club.  We now have 8 sets of clubs in the "golf closet." thats like our bikes...(we have 13 bikes)lol...wow. 
tommorow we get to dissect crayfish. My bio teacher thinks i need to be a surgeon because last time we did disections i managed to perfectly remove all the skin from our specimen without noticing because i was bored.  It ended up being the class demo for a good dissection procedure.  I got lucky is all im saying.
ttyl

IM studying for my ap hist test and desperatly need a distraction. Today was boring...nothing happened. we did dissections in bio but thats it. Next summer im going to Miami right after JOs. Ill be there w/ some freinds and no family for a week and a half (his dad is coming) and then a bunch over other of our freinds (12 to be axact 14 in all) fly down and join us for a day then we get on two sailboats and sail to Key west. 3 day trip down 1 day in Key west 3 day trip back. its gonna be awesome.while were there we can either go to margaritaville or hard rock cafe.

POLL: Which should i go to?
       Margaritaville
       Hard Rock Cafe
(im gettin t shirts from both neways so which is cooler and has better food?)
We ran today for the first time in a couple months....enough said. im gonna hobble back to the basketball game now.

Just got back from Florida. It was awesome as usual.  played alot of golf, went to the beach like everyday, met some cool ppl at the pool. Got sunburn. Bu it was cool.  We went body boarding at the beach and some waves on friday were def. massive. bug enough to knock me off and bruise my leg gainst some shells.  the drive was horrible.  12 hrs. w/ a lot of ppl in 1 car = bad.  But at least i watched some movies. (thanks JB) but yeah... i dont want to go bk to school. and im not ready to start swimming again either. The pope died today. he was a cool guy if u really think ab it, whether ur catholic or not.  He did so much for everyone, not only catholics.  but neways. im out...i gotta study some stuff, and watch some basket ball...peace.

good day today.  my mom told me shed help pay for most of my new paintball gun (tourneys start next month)swimming was awesome...we played waterpolo today.  That is definately one of the roughest contact sports ever. My right eye is swelling shut, my lip bled most of the time, and my nose is swollen, and i have scratches up and down my back and stomach.  i hit lia's eye and its swelled and i feel pretty bad ab that. It was good tho...again tommorow.
-peace

So this weekend was actually pretty good.  Friday night i went to watch scetionals.  Saturday I went to the YMCA, bestbuy and the mall. Then i was supposed to meet some ppl for the bobcats game in the foodcourt.  Then someone kept calling my name and i was really confused but it ended up being alexa, brianna, kristi, and natalie.  So i talked with them for a while while and waited for everyone to show up. waited (o and earlier in a magazine store, i was buying a twix bar and the black guy in front of me was buying  a playgirl...........)Finally we all left for the bball game....the girls wanted to come...but it was a very very good thing they didnt.  We get to the game...in line to get tickets and they tell us that they ran out of 10.00 ones and none of us had enough $ to buy $30.00.  So we left.  (we knew that vanful of mexicans would beat us to the ticket line.) we sat in the parking lot for like 20 minutes deciding what to do...so we decide to go bowling.  Brent didnt know how to get there from the coliseum so he took a really long way...hwy 51 instead of 4-85.  so we get there like 20 min after everyone else.  its 7:15.  We go inside and wait in line for a half an hour....7:45  THEN the guy comes and says sorry but theres b-day parties goin on and the league is in the other room so we can get all 12 of you ONE LANE AT 9:45.   we were like screw that. so we waited in the parking lot trying to ecide what to do...30 minutes later a cop pulls up and tells us to disperse because we were 'essentially loitering' by trying to decide what to do.  so we stand there for like 5 ore minutes trying to figure out what the hells goin on...so we all just give up and are like screw it lets go home... so the ppl with no ride home are basically screwed, because all our parents were out at movies w/ cellphones off thinking that mrs. baskwell would bring us home after the game we were  supposed to be at.  so we end up cramming six ppl into mike biehl's truck and he takes us back to brian nelsons house :( so me greg JP and brian show up at his house and play basketball till midnight after we spent like 45 minutes getting a hold of our parents and stuff.  spent the night....went to breakfast home. Interesting night.  Today i played my new xbox game Brothers in Arms which rocks. then i worked out a little ran and went to the golf course..driving range for an hour... home for hw then down to huntersville for the last night of finals. now i just wasted a really long time typing this so i gotta finish hw...peace

But im not gonna let any more cuts get away from me by .2 of a second.  I ate tacos for dinner...so that was good...im gonna watch lost so thatl be good. Wow, its been the longest weekend.  I swam great at the meet, but missed my sectional cuts by .2 of a second in the 100 and 200 fly.  Saturday I went to lunch @ Qdoba wit Jnathan, Chandler, Joseph, Alexa, Brianna, and Bryanna. I broke 3 forks trying to eat my burrito.  Then casey came in, and I ended up going to her house with the girls.  We watched a modern rendition of Romeo and Juliet, with guns, cars, etc.  i thought it was hilarious.  Imean,its a sad story, but they killed it.  I laughed alot, so did everyone else....besides casey, who cried.  any ways, now ive gotta finish my Homework, sleep, eat, eat, and eat.
Peace, good luck at sectionals sectional ppl.
